div class=page_classes
  h1 class=page_title = t("pages.terms_agreement.title")

  p.mb-4
    | ユーザー登録には利用規約への同意が必要です。
  .w-96.terms-box.border.border-blue-300.rounded.bg-blue-300.p-4.bg-light.mb-4.flex.justify-center.items-center
      = link_to '利用規約はこちら', terms_path, target: '_blank', rel: 'noopener'
  = form_with url: new_user_registration_path, method: :get do |f|
    .form-check.flex.items-center.justify-center.mb-4
      = f.check_box :agreed, id: 'agreement_check'
      = f.label :agreed, '上記の利用規約に同意します', for: 'agreement_check'
    = f.submit t("pages.terms_agreement.submit_button"), class: button_classes, id: 'register_button'
